snippet.textDisplay:
I LOVE THIS COMMERCIAL. It is so adorable and heartwarming! The use of "You're My Best Friend" by Queen is also AMAZING. If they didn't use that song, I actually had another idea for a song they could use: "Happy Together", for a couple of reasons:
1. The band who sings it is The Turtles. Squirtle is the Tiny Turtle Pokémon.
2. The lyrics of the chorus: "I can't see me lovin' nobody but you for all my life/When you're with me, baby the skies will be blue, for all my life". It fits the commercial!
3. It was actually used in the marketing for the Detective Pikachu movie back during the hype season of the film, if you remember!
snippet.textOriginal:

2. The lyrics of the chorus: "I can't see me lovin' nobody but you for all my life/When you're with me, baby the skies will be blue, for all my life". It fits the commercial!

snippet.textDisplay:
Everyone keeps saying "My childhood!" or "Right in the feels!" but in all truth, this is why they keep trying to promote Kanto and push their lame "Kanto agenda" on us. To get to emotional "millenials" like almost everyone here. They are milking the cash cow at this point and I am utterly sick and tired of anything Kanto. It is overkill now. Not "emotional" not "cute" for me. Just plain money grubbing and cow milking.

We have over 7 other gens full of Pokemon, but because millenials still play and make up most of the players as well as the dough, they cater to them market wise mostly screwing over every other gen. The reason Charizard is every where still is because GF is desperate for money so they literally are trying to stick with the original 150 to get their original players who also have kids now. Sorry, but I am over Kanto. I am sick of all the pandering to Kanto now since X and Y. They need to move tf on and give spotlight to other Pokemon gens too. Their "glory" days are over.

Doing once a decade? Promoting childhood memories? Amazing and yes, emotional. Worth seeing whatever the promotion or commercial is. Constantly doing it every year and with the new generation? Pathetic and boring now.

Can't wait to see the D/P remake have nothing but new Kanto forms!
